  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/f9fbe707b2ebe19a5f2aaa234655e2e6.avif?t=1772367169\" width=1560 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world of spherical, fluffy animals, you set sail to rescue the Mouse Queen’s cook from the clutches of the alligators. You will encounter challenging sea battles, picturesque island landscapes, and ships that only exist in a world of fluffy animal pirates.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/c21dec4359f3551caa6f4b503c407099.poster.avif?t=1772367169\" width=960 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/c21dec4359f3551caa6f4b503c407099.webm?t=1772367169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/c21dec4359f3551caa6f4b503c407099.mp4?t=1772367169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/1ba05be8dfa5eae8a6ffc549bbff9ca1.avif?t=1772367169\" width=1560 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not everyone is as infallible as the Mouse Queen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a defeat, you return to the Mouse Kingdom to improve your skills and make another attempt. Keep getting stronger until you can rule the seas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/fc605ae108258c52c833d688d99f6e55.poster.avif?t=1772367169\" width=960 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/fc605ae108258c52c833d688d99f6e55.webm?t=1772367169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/fc605ae108258c52c833d688d99f6e55.mp4?t=1772367169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/2a9749c7f154b46c2921aa90890d1b07.avif?t=1772367169\" width=1560 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your enemies surrender, you can add them to your fleet and benefit from their different designs and strengths!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/fdd95cf0f397d3e89ebf5912560eaa4a.poster.avif?t=1772367169\" width=960 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/fdd95cf0f397d3e89ebf5912560eaa4a.webm?t=1772367169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/fdd95cf0f397d3e89ebf5912560eaa4a.mp4?t=1772367169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What are you waiting for? The Mouse Queen has chosen you as her champion! Set sail and rescue the royal cook. Nobody likes bad food. Nobody.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/f9fbe707b2ebe19a5f2aaa234655e2e6.avif?t=1772367169\" width=1560 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world of spherical, fluffy animals, you set sail to rescue the Mouse Queen’s cook from the clutches of the alligators. You will encounter challenging sea battles, picturesque island landscapes, and ships that only exist in a world of fluffy animal pirates.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/c21dec4359f3551caa6f4b503c407099.poster.avif?t=1772367169\" width=960 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/c21dec4359f3551caa6f4b503c407099.webm?t=1772367169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/c21dec4359f3551caa6f4b503c407099.mp4?t=1772367169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/1ba05be8dfa5eae8a6ffc549bbff9ca1.avif?t=1772367169\" width=1560 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not everyone is as infallible as the Mouse Queen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a defeat, you return to the Mouse Kingdom to improve your skills and make another attempt. Keep getting stronger until you can rule the seas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/fc605ae108258c52c833d688d99f6e55.poster.avif?t=1772367169\" width=960 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/fc605ae108258c52c833d688d99f6e55.webm?t=1772367169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/fc605ae108258c52c833d688d99f6e55.mp4?t=1772367169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/2a9749c7f154b46c2921aa90890d1b07.avif?t=1772367169\" width=1560 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your enemies surrender, you can add them to your fleet and benefit from their different designs and strengths!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/fdd95cf0f397d3e89ebf5912560eaa4a.poster.avif?t=1772367169\" width=960 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/fdd95cf0f397d3e89ebf5912560eaa4a.webm?t=1772367169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887350/extras/fdd95cf0f397d3e89ebf5912560eaa4a.mp4?t=1772367169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What are you waiting for? The Mouse Queen has chosen you as her champion! Set sail and rescue the royal cook. Nobody likes bad food. Nobody.</p>",
